===Analysis===
Priority: '''Low'''
:A German destroyer with performance comparable to a [[Fubuki]]-class' first remodel, albeit with a bit weaker Torpedo stat.
:Her ASW stat allows her to perform OASW at high-but-before-marriage levels with proper gear.
